  "description": [
    "Page Four Americas Most Revolting Scandals Are In Washingtons Public Schools Dr Carl F Hansen Superintendent An AllOut Race Mixer Is Yelling For Help The greatest scandal in America to day is found in the public schools of the nations capital hi an article discussing the situation recently U S NEWS WORLD RE PORT entitled its article The Blight in the Nations Capital A citizens com mittee composed of both white and Negro citizens recently described the school situation as being in a state of chaos Crime is rampant in the schools Dr Carl F Hansen the public school superintendent in Washington has been defending the system in recent years but now comes out and asks for authori ty to expel all the troublemakers Teachers Need Help Recently he said Teachers have reached the breaking point From all of the reports I have gotten they need help He says that the overall situation has become worse in the last year or two Last Thanksgiving Day a race riot took place at the new District of Co lumbia Stadium where a team of all Negroes was playing a team mostly white When the Negro team lost the Negroes stormed the white"
